00:26:28.060 --> 00:26:29.960
And so that they
don't limit you,

00:26:29.960 --> 00:26:31.870
and not only do
they not limit you,

00:26:31.870 --> 00:26:38.330
but you thrive in an environment
that's not very welcoming.

00:26:38.330 --> 00:26:44.690
LUPITA NYONG'O: Well, Yeah, so.

00:26:44.690 --> 00:26:53.720
I-- I always credit
my parents because-- I

00:26:53.720 --> 00:26:59.220
