00:46:15.850 --> 00:46:18.040
then we're not
telling a true story.

00:46:18.040 --> 00:46:19.170
And it's not compelling.

00:46:19.170 --> 00:46:20.830
That's the irony, right?

00:46:20.830 --> 00:46:23.500
The more we make it like
not truthful to who we are,

00:46:23.500 --> 00:46:26.440
and what we do, and the
specifics of our culture, then

00:46:26.440 --> 00:46:29.630
the less we actually create
something that's compelling.

00:46:29.630 --> 00:46:31.852
And so, it's really
like, we have to-- I

00:46:31.852 --> 00:46:35.860
do always pursue authenticity
and accessibility.

00:46:35.860 --> 00:46:38.070
