00:46:41.190 --> 00:46:45.160
will dilute it for us
if we are not vigilant.

00:46:45.160 --> 00:46:49.850
And part of, I think,
what we are after is,

00:46:49.850 --> 00:46:51.440
once and for all,
for God's sake,

00:46:51.440 --> 00:46:53.300
is seeing something
specific when

00:46:53.300 --> 00:46:56.430
it comes to African
storytelling on stage, right?

00:46:56.430 --> 00:46:59.930
The accent is actually
from the region, the music,

00:46:59.930 --> 00:47:02.600
the clothes-- you know that
it's not-- so many times

00:47:02.600 --> 00:47:07.440
I've seen something
that's about East Africa

00:47:07.440 --> 00:47:09.640
and there's ladies with
black mambazo playing, which

00:47:09.640 --> 00:47:11.070
