I have to turn it off

00:47:13.070 --> 00:47:14.950
because I can't get involved.

00:47:14.950 --> 00:47:19.120
It's just, if they didn't
make the effort, you know.

00:47:19.120 --> 00:47:21.910
If you're making a French
film and suddenly you

00:47:21.910 --> 00:47:25.500
hear Russian music playing,
it doesn't make any sense.

00:47:25.500 --> 00:47:30.150
And we need the same level
of specificity and respect.

00:47:30.150 --> 00:47:35.900
So, for me, why this is
successful is because we--

00:47:35.900 --> 00:47:40.610
we're uncompromising in
the search for specificity.

00:47:40.610 --> 00:47:43.665
Because other people can do
the other thing, and have.

00:47:43.665 --> 00:47:45.540
DANAI GURIRA: It is a
